reviewText: Great DVD of ICW, goes well with the others released by Jadat Sports on ICW. Very good, and shows why wrestling was the King of Sports then.

Wrestling fans who remember Ronnie Garvin, Randy Savage, Angelo Poffo and other Gulf Coast Legends will definitely want to add this DVD to your collection of memories. To see history in the making will bring the rush of enthusiasm that we used to feel when tuned into the action on our TV sets. To have a video like this should certainly make the owners feel proud to be wrestling fans.
IT TELLS YOU WHAT YOUR UP FOR AND THAT WHAT U GET. WRESTLING OLD-SCHOOL AT IT'S BEST!

A mix of Angelo Poffo's ICW, (mostly from the later days), and a bit of Randy Savage's Memphis run. Would have liked to have seen more early ICW, (the Mizer, the Devil's Duo... so on), but it's still a disc worth having.
